ession/ext/normal/7b/2024_takearest_org.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;边吃饭边玩手机，会越来越胖啊？？&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;真的会！吃饭时分心玩手机，会让你的注意力全在手机上，不仅影响食物消化，还会延长你的吃饭的时间，让你不知不觉越吃越多，更容易长胖哦&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[doge]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%E9%97%AE%E7%AD%94%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%E9%97%AE%E7%AD%94%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#小卫辟谣问答#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;（科普中国）&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;劝是劝了，听不听你随意&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[在线等]&quot; src=&quot;https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/87/2024_bewaitingonline_org.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hvco5mqgndj20gg0fk3zi.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;</description><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/OF1v0vDy6</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://weibo.com/2831150640/OF1v0vDy6</guid><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 09:57:34 GMT</pubDate><author>深圳卫健委</author><category>小卫辟谣问答</category></item></channel></rss>